'''''Nta Zahabu kuri Kalsaka''''' ( [[Igifaransa|Igifaransa:]] '''''Pas d'or pour Kalsaka''''' ) ni film documentaire ya [[Burukina Faso|Burkina faso]] ya 2019 yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Michel K. Zongo kandi afatanije na Florian Schewe. <ref name="Crew">https://www.crew-united.com/en/No-Gold-for-Kalsaka__249791.html</ref> <ref name="Akh">https://en.akhbar1.com/no-gold-for-kalsaka-a-burkina-faso-community-s-lost-land-37242.html</ref>

== Umusaruro ==
Gufata amashusho byakorewe mu ntara ya Yatenga muri [[Burukina Faso|Burkinafaso]] . Yakozwe na Michel K. Zongo muri Diam Production [bf] na Florian Schewe muri Film Five GmbH. <ref name="Main">https://www.filmfive.net/no-gold-for-kalsaka.html</ref> 

== Umugambi / Icegeranyo ==
Kuva kera, mu gihugu cya Afurika cya [[Burukina Faso|Burkina Faso]], abaturage bo mu mudugudu muto wa Kalsaka bari baracukuye kandi bakoresha zahabu mu rwego rwo kubatunga. Hamwe n’ishirahamwe ry’abongereza rishinzwe ubucukuzi bw’amabuye y’amahanga, ariko, ibyo byaje kurangira kuko abaturage bari barahawe akarere kavuye mu bucukuzi bw'amabuye y'agaciro mu butaka bwabo. Umuganda wumudugudu, nyamara, uyobowe na Jean-Baptiste, urwana cyane kugirango ugarure ibye. <ref name="Main">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.filmfive.net/no-gold-for-kalsaka.html "No Gold for Kalsaka | Documentary | By Michael K Zongo"]. Film Five<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">November 12,</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>  <ref name="Akh" />

