== Kwakira ==
Ku ya 15 Ugushyingo 2019 ku bufatanye n’iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya documentaire rya Montreal (RIDM), iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere na Sinema Politica Concordia i Quebec . <ref>https://www.concordia.ca/cuevents/main/2019/11/15/cinema-politica-presents-no-gold-for-kalsaka-with-director-michel-k-zongo.html</ref> Iyi filime yemejwe ko ari imwe muri filime zihindura isi kandi byari biteganijwe ko izerekanwa bwa mbere muri [[Cekiya|Ceki]] muri Autumn 2020 na ''One World'' . <ref>https://www.oneworld.cz/2020/films-a-z/40666</ref>

